episodes.description: Candice Kumai, a renowned influencer of wellness, visits her mother's home country Japan to reconfirm and share her philosophies of well-being which are inspired by Japanese traditions and spirits.
episodes.subtitle: Ep 1 "kintsugi"
episodes.title: Kintsugi Wellness

episodes.description: Candice Kumai AKA "the golden girl of wellness" has been striving to live up to her expectations in Kyoto, she discovers the beauty of kintsugi and learns that it's okay to be broken and mended.
episodes.subtitle: Ep 2 "broken"
episodes.title: Kintsugi Wellness
